data.title: 2013 Currie Cup First Division
data.meta_description: The 2013 Currie Cup First Division was contested from 29 June to 11 October 2013. The tournament is the second tier of South Africa's premier domestic rugby union competition, featuring teams representing either entire provinces or substantial regions within provinces.
